biography: Experienced change manager with extensive operational experience in customer-oriented organizations in Transport, Retail and FMCG. Powerful in aligning stakeholders, especially in highly complex environments and always with an IT component. Likes to aim for results on a human-oriented way in a step-by-step approach. Always with lot of enthusiasm.
